      "name": "Calendar Clone (extends Calendar)",
      "images": [],
      "summary": "The CalendarClone component extends the base Calendar to provide a user interface for creating and managing calendar events. It allows users to select the current date, input event titles and times, and add new events to the calendar. The component tracks user input and updates the calendar's list of events dynamically. Its primary purpose is to facilitate interactive event creation and display within a calendar environment, enhancing user engagement with calendar data.",
